query:
SELECT 
  p.challengeId,
  SUM(CASE WHEN p.gender = 'male' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as maleCount,
  SUM(CASE WHEN p.gender = 'female' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as femaleCount,
  SUM(CASE WHEN p.gender = 'unspecified' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as unspecifiedCount
FROM participations p
WHERE p.deletedAt IS NULL
GROUP BY p.challengeId
LIMIT 10;
